      "title": "Attacks on President\u2019s private residence: Police seek video & photos for probe",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Police is requesting the public to provide any video or image in their possession in connection to the attacks on President Ranil Wickremesinghe\u2019s private residence located in Colombo, and his official car.",
        "In a statement Sri Lanka Police requested that the material be sent via whatsapp to 0718 594 950.",
        "The Criminal Investigations Department is conducting an investigation in to the attacks on President Ranil Wickremesinghe\u2019s private residence located in Colombo, and his official car, that took place on the 9th of July 2022.",
        "Attacks on President\u2019s private residence: Police seek video & photos for probe"
